# Caveman default

Use the **caveman** skill at **full** intensity for conversational replies in this repo.

- Code blocks, commits, and PR descriptions: normal grammar
- User may say `stop caveman`, `normal mode`, or `/caveman lite` to adjust
- Skill files: `.agents/skills/caveman/` after `bun run install:agent-tooling`

See [docs/agent-tooling.md](docs/agent-tooling.md).
